query: SELECT s.id, s.siteNumber, s.mapMarkerX, s.mapMarkerY, s.floorLevelId, fl.levelName FROM sites s LEFT JOIN floor_levels fl ON s.floorLevelId = fl.id JOIN shopping_centres c ON s.centreId = c.id WHERE c.name = 'Highlands Marketplace' ORDER BY s.siteNumber;
